name: Internet DealBook

overview:
Internet DealBook is a repository of information about Internet- and technology-related investments and M&A deals. Founded in 2011, we aim to provide an extensive list of deals from around the world.

Our publisher, Online Agility, has been informally tracking internet- and technology-related deals for a long time and many people have asked us about internet- and technology-related investments and M&A deals. We had been looking for a site to share, but while there are lots of great news sites which track breaking news and provide detailed analysis on a specific deal, we couldn’t find a simple site providing an extensive listing of top deals, ranked by size, or grouped by various sectors and geographies.

That’s why we set out to build a site whose mission is to provide an extensive list of internet- and technology-related investments and M&A deals in the world!

We hope you find the site useful so if you have any feedback and suggestions please drop us a note and let us know how we can make our site and newsletters better.

Internet DealBook is published by Online Agility, a Right Click Capital company.
